snippet.title: Rocket League Sideswipe Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Rocket League Sideswipe Gameplay Trailer! Visit https://www.Twitter.com/RLSideswipe for more details.

Get charged up for Rocket League Sideswipe, the new standalone mobile game from Psyonix! Prepare to hit the pitch like never before, in this twist on Rocket League action from a new perspective. 

Download now on iOS and Android and get in the game from anywhere. Rocket League Sideswipe features intuitive touch controls and controller support. Hit your boost to go faster, or use it to get off the ground and into the air to pull off some amazing aerial maneuvers. Enjoy Private Matches with friends, or play Competitive Matches online with players around the world. Climb your way up the Competitive Ranks, and even crack the worldwide leaderboard!

Look out for the beginning of Season 1 in December!

Follow us at https://www.Twitter.com/RLSideswipe

Rocket League Sideswipe Gameplay Trailer
https://youtu.be/1knKmT4N-ZY

#RocketLeague #RocketLeagueSideswipe #RocketLeagueSideswipeTrailer
